OL,3,CWhy illegal e-bikes could provide
OL,4,Cclues for police tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FSargent Andrew Walton said: "A big
OL,8,Fsign is the stuck on conversion kits,
OL,9,Fwhich are usually held on with a bit
OL,10,Fof duct tape.
OL,12,F"You can tell that it used to be just
OL,13,Fa normal pedal cycle, but it's been
OL,14,Fillegally adapted with a home
OL,15,Fconversion kit to make it go faster.
OL,17,F"We are aware that delivery drivers
OL,18,Ffor example that don't have permission
OL,19,Fto work in the UK may end up getting
OL,20,Fexploited by others, as this isn't
OL,21,Fcontrolled in the gig economy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
