OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"So there is a step into serious and
OL,8,Forganised crime and part of my team
OL,9,Fare trained up as modern slavery
OL,10,Fvictim liaison officers."
OL,12,FPolice inspector Nathan Johnson said:
OL,13,F"People are brought over to the UK on
OL,14,Fthe promise of a job, and then when
OL,15,Fthey get here they're paid some money
OL,16,Fand they're then in debt to someone
OL,17,Fwho is then asking them to ride and
OL,18,Fmake money for someone else, and then
OL,19,Fthey can't get themselves out of it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
