OL,3,CWhy illegal e-bikes could provide
OL,4,Cclues for police tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"Although we are stopping riders,
OL,8,Foften the riders are exploited, so it
OL,9,Fis about safeguarding people."
OL,11,FDuring a day of action, officers were
OL,12,Fjoined by an immigration enforcement
OL,13,Fteam. They seized 8 illegally adapted
OL,14,Fe-bikes and two e-scooters.
OL,16,FAs well as safeguarding, officers say
OL,17,Fthey also want to protect the public.
