OL,3,CWhy illegal e-bikes could provide
OL,4,Cclues for police tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FRegulations state that pedal assist e-
OL,8,Fbikes should cut out at 15mph and
OL,9,Ftwist and go throttles shouldn't allow
OL,10,Fthem to go more than 3.5mph. Some e-
OL,11,Fbikes they've found have exceeded
OL,12,Fspeeds of 60mph.
OL,14,FSargent Andrew Walton added: "The risk
OL,15,Fof serious injury to members of the
OL,16,Fpublic can be quite high if they
OL,17,Ftravel too fast.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
