OL,3,CWhy illegal e-bikes could provide
OL,4,Cclues for police tackling organised
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"If it was involved in an accident it
OL,8,Fgets classified as a non-insured motor
OL,9,Fvehicle, and this is part of the
OL,10,Freason why insurance premiums go up
OL,11,Feach year. So an increase in e-bikes
OL,12,Fhas a correlation to the increase in
OL,13,Fpremium people pay on their own
OL,14,Fpersonal insurance."
